                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9095" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0267</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1267 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">曙光股份中小股东的逆袭之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Reversal Path of Minority Shareholders in Shuguang Stock</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杨宏玲，赵浩然</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">辽宁曙光汽车集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">关联交易；中小股东；临时股东大会；决议效力</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Related-party transactions, Minority shareholders, Extraordinary General Meeting, Resolution validity</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">曙光股份的一项关联交易引发了中小股东的强烈反对。在尝试通过董事会寻求解决方案未果后，中小股东中的七位召集人自行召集临时股东大会，并作出了终止关联交易、选举产生新一届董事会成员的决议。但原董事会认为临时股东大会的召开不符合法律规定，因此会议作出的全部 22 项决议不能产生法律效力，形成了两个董事会并存的状况。针对临时股东大会决议的有效性产生了五起诉讼，法院最终确认了临时股东大会决议的有效性。此案例主要描述中小股东如何通过临时股东大会维护自身权益。通过此案例，可以学习公司治理中临时股东大会的召集程序、影响股东大会决议效力的因素以及中小股东保护自身权益的途径，进一步理解我国公司法实施 30 年对我国现代企业制度建立的重要作用。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">A related-party transaction involving Shuguang Stock has triggered strong opposition from minority shareholders. After their attempts to seek a resolution through the board of directors failed, seven conveners among the minority shareholders independently called an Extraordinary General Meeting (EGM) and passed resolutions to terminate the related-party transaction and elect a new board of directors. However, the original board deemed the EGM to be legally non-compliant, asserting that all 22 resolutions passed at the meeting were legally ineffective, resulting in the coexistence of two boards of directors. This led to five lawsuits regarding the validity of the EGM resolutions. Ultimately, the court confirmed the validity of the EGM resolutions. This case primarily describes how minority shareholders protected their rights through the EGM. Through this case, one can learn about the procedures for convening an EGM in corporate governance, the factors affecting the validity of shareholders&#39; meeting resolutions, and the ways minority shareholders can protect their rights, further understanding the significant role of the Company Law in establishing modern corporate systems over the past 30 years in China.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司治理》、《商法》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">董事会、股东会在公司治理中的作用；控股股东权利滥用；临时股东会召集人及召开程序；股东会决议效力及其撤销机制。</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-01</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
